<section class="reviews mod book-content">
    <header>
        <a href="new_review" rel="nofollow" class="create-review redbutt rr" 
            data-isverify="False"
            data-verify-url="https://www.douban.com/accounts/phone/verify?redir=https://book.douban.com/subject/1390240/new_review">
            <span>我要写书评</span>
        </a>
        <h2>
            论“神圣”的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 1 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7693171">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7693171/" class="title-link">值得一看的一本书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7693171"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/watcher3/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2610176-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/watcher3/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">watcher</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-12-16"
      class="main-meta">2015-12-16 16:31:03</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7693171_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  神圣作为宗教的一个范畴，有其深刻的非理性的一面。但我个人并不觉得作者是在“剔除掉神圣观念中的道德与理性因素”，而是在于挖掘其中的被人们长期忽视的非理性因素，这种挖掘这并不妨碍神圣中的理性因素。神圣包含着理性与非理性，是一种挑选、一种区别，为神所挑选，区别于...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            中国社会科学出版社2009版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7693171_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7693171_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评1篇
                </a>
            </p>
</section>
    
